              "message": "D1 says `external_guides.py` is the only current Python caller of `atomic_write.py`, but the roadmap ADR still treats `track_registry.py` as another caller. As written, this makes the deletion chain incomplete: removing `atomic_write.py` here would strand an existing caller unless Phase 1 is part of the same change set.",
