              "category": "contradiction"
            },
            {
              "message": "D2 asks for semantic edits to the already-merged roadmap ADR (body note plus decision metadata changes). That conflicts with `knowledge/conventions/pre-track-adr-authoring.md`, which only allows post-merge ADR edits for typos, broken cross-references, or adding a back-reference. The supersede should be expressed without rewriting the merged ADR's decision state.",
